{"tid":762530,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"完全看不出來原來用的是「地攤貨」…BLACKPINK造型師發威！造型瞬間看來超高級","createTime":"2018-07-31T11:07:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-31T11:18:44.000Z","uid":51412,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"41f1e924db9d601f259a7176e3c54b9039a88904","tid":762530,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:07:59.000Z","msg":"完全看不出來原來用的是「地攤貨」&hellip;BLACKPINK造型師發威！造型瞬間看來超高級<br />\n<br />\n地攤貨只要這樣搭&hellip;瞬間也能變高級！YG造型師超威<br />\n<br />\n雖然大家都知道造型師是辛苦的職業，不僅常要配合偶像早出晚歸的行程，常到深夜才有空為偶像量製衣服，到了回歸前更是為了舞台服裝而絞盡腦汁，但每當看到偶像被穿上難以理解的時尚時，粉絲似乎還是會暫時理智斷線，忘了造型師的辛勞而開罵<br />\n<br />\n不過有批評有進步(？)，似乎就是Red Velvet造型的最佳例子，從過去被說「亂搭名牌」，到現在總算找出適合成員的服裝類型，不得不說看得出來造型師是真的有在求進步。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DiEOYYh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDiEOYYh.png&h=436783a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過要說到女團造型師中的霸主(？)，還是不得不提BLACKPINK的造型師了，不只當初曾<br />\n被拿來和Red Velvet的造型師比較，說「同一套衣服，搭起來卻差超多」，成了刺激Red<br />\nVelvet造型師進步的原動力(？)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/0tCMt12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F0tCMt12.jpg&h=10bd29b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBLACKPINK成員在不發片的時候被稱為「網美」，總是擅長各式的穿搭讓她們贏得「行走<br />\n香奈兒」、「行走Gucci」美稱的造型師更是功不可沒！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bpWq5OEbwhQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbpWq5OEbwhQ&d=srOU00ChBn%2FrmsnY%2FJTeJ9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c8a63c9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bpWq5OEbwhQ</a><br />\n<br />\n不過BLACKPINK的造型師擅長穿搭的功力在最近又再度讓網友驚豔，因為成員的打歌服不<br />\n只搭配得好，就連各式的配飾也讓人出乎意料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LTw4hN0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLTw4hN0.jpg&h=a1b44b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n因為不只Jisoo頭上的髮飾明顯就是會擺在你書桌上的別針，讓人忍不住想大喊Jisoo千萬<br />\n要小心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tyO1LG8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtyO1LG8.png&h=ea76d0d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成員Lisa的髮飾雖然比較溫合一點，但是鏡頭拉近一看，原以為是五顏六色髮夾的裝飾&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/HyO9F8q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FHyO9F8q.png&h=df7ca106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n竟然是迴紋針來著XDDDD...髮飾真相不只讓人忍不住想讚嘆BLACKPINK造型師的想像力，<br />\n也忍不住佩服她們的造型師，連文具都可以玩出新花樣，本來就設計給人穿(？)的衣服難<br />\n不倒他們也是意料之中了啦！"},{"pid":"2ebff768d2bfbcd18786a0c20d4cfbc76bcb2710","tid":762530,"uid":85557,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:18:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://erpimgs.idealhere.com/ImageFormal/8d/cd/f4/8dcdf481-b941-4ae9-8442-0da97c15ce4c/heads/600x600/25bd5777-79a2-443e-97e5-7a53cd1db321.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ferpimgs.idealhere.com%2FImageFormal%2F8d%2Fcd%2Ff4%2F8dcdf481-b941-4ae9-8442-0da97c15ce4c%2Fheads%2F600x600%2F25bd5777-79a2-443e-97e5-7a53cd1db321.jpg&h=e45b78fa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}